
EXPLORING DATA
- evaluate crowd wisdom by looking at if a decrease or increase in opening to closing is correlated with outcome

OUTCOMES 
- Win or loss (classification)
- Points (for betting the odds, betting the line, and the over under.
- Line 
- 1st, 2nd, 3rd, 4th quarter points

FEATURES
- using difference between opening and closing line to harness information from crowd wisdom.- look at 
- previous game(s) stats, previous mkt performance. 

SCRIPT
- in a shiny appp - choose and outcome (tab, scroll down) and (1) look at that outcomes relationship with the features, (2) Look at how it did with each model - accuracy, how much money it would have won you by choosing a train and test window, (3) look at how much money it actually won you.



